<!DOCTYPE html>
<html dir="rtl" lang="ar">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>مشاهدة: <%= course.title %></title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.rtl.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cairo:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Cairo', sans-serif; background: #0f172a; color: white; min-height: 100vh; }
        .video-container { 
            position: relative; padding-bottom: 56.25%; height: 0; overflow: hidden; 
            border-radius: 20px; background: #000; box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
        }
        .video-container iframe { position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; border: 0; }
        .back-btn { color: #6366f1; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; transition: 0.3s; }
        .back-btn:hover { color: white; }
        .course-info { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); border-radius: 15px; padding: 20px; margin-top: 20px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container py-5">
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-4">
            <h2 class="fw-bold text-primary"><%= course.title %></h2>
            <a href="/home" class="back-btn"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right me-2"></i> العودة للرئيسية</a>
        </div>

        <div class="video-container">
            <iframe 
                src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/<%= course.vid %>?rel=0&modestbranding=1" 
                allowfullscreen>
            </iframe>
        </div>

        <div class="course-info shadow-sm">
            <h4><i class="fas fa-info-circle me-2"></i> تفاصيل المحتوى</h4>
            <p class="text-secondary mb-0">أنت الآن تشاهد محتوى "<strong><%= course.title %></strong>". تأكد من جودة الإنترنت لديك للمشاهدة بدون تقطيع.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
